# Portfolio — Gabriel Costa

**Status:** Under construction  
**Planned publication date:** **06/02/2025 (February 6, 2025)**

This repository contains the website for my professional portfolio, focused on projects and analyses for the financial market. The full version will be published on **February 6, 2025**.

**What will be available at publication**
- **About section** with experience and core competencies.  
- **Power BI dashboard projects** with descriptions and usage examples.  
- **Financial audit reports** including methodologies and findings, published with fully anonymized data.  
- **SQL Server projects** with sample queries, data modeling, and optimization notes.  
- **Automated ETL projects with Python** including scripts, pipeline descriptions, and execution instructions.  
- **Professional contact and proposal form** for institutional inquiries.  
- **Supporting materials**: reports, dashboards, and code examples.

**Repository structure (expected)**
- `index.html` — public site (when published).  
- `assets/` — images, logos, and static files.  
- `projects/` — folders for each project, notebooks, and reports.  
- `docs/` — technical documentation and methodologies.

**Privacy and data handling**
Any reports or examples that include real data will be published only after **complete anonymization** to protect sensitive information and comply with confidentiality requirements.

**Contact**
For urgent inquiries or institutional proposals, email **gabriel@seudominio.com** or visit **https://gabrielcostaeconomista-specportifoliodeprojetos/**.

Thank you for visiting — the complete portfolio will be available soon.
